PROJECT CONTEXT PROMPT (PAINTINGS / DIGITAL MUSEUM APP)

I am building a full-stack Digital Museum / Paintings Gallery web app.

🧠 STACK
Frontend
React + TypeScript (Vite)
Chakra UI
Framer Motion
React Router
Backend
Node.js + Express
MongoDB Atlas (Mongoose)
Winston logging (structured logging system implemented)
🏛 CURRENT ARCHITECTURE
API
GET /api/paintings → fetch all paintings
GET /api/paintings/:id → fetch single painting (with related paintings populated)
Static Images
Served via Express:
/paintings → maps to local image folder
📦 DATA MODEL (Mongoose)

Painting schema:

title
artist
year
medium
description
imageUrls (array)
tags (array)
relatedPaintings (ObjectId refs → self-referencing via populate)
