🎨 DATASET

24 total paintings seeded:

Classical + Romanticism + Renaissance + Symbolism + Baroque + Realism
Includes Goya, Klimt, Delacroix, Rembrandt, Michelangelo, Leonardo, etc.
“Saturn Devouring His Son” replaced with “The Sleep of Reason Produces Monsters”
🧠 GRAPH SYSTEM (IMPORTANT FEATURE)

We built a relationship engine:

buildRelationships.js
compares every painting with every other painting
computes similarity score using:
same artist (+5)
shared art movement (+4 per match)
shared tags (+2 per tag)
keyword overlap in description
stores top related paintings in MongoDB (relatedPaintings array)
📊 GRAPH EXPORT SYSTEM
exportGraph.js
converts MongoDB paintings into:
{
  nodes: [{ id, title, artist }],
  links: [{ source, target }]
}
outputs graph.json used by frontend visualization
🌐 FRONTEND STATE

Pages:

Landing page (animated)
Gallery page (search + grid)
Painting details page (shows related paintings)
Graph page (/graph) → force-directed graph visualization
🧠 GRAPH VISUALIZATION

We use:

react-force-graph-2d

Features:

nodes = paintings
links = relationships
click node → navigate to painting details
colored clusters by artist
interactive physics simulation

Current improvements:

improved node visibility
link styling
force simulation tuning
labels rendered via canvas

